data.meta_description:
5 likes, 0 comments - brynmawrfilminstitute on June 18, 2024: "THELMA (2024)⁠
⁠
Starts this Friday, June 21!⁠
⁠
When 93-year-old Thelma is conned by a scammer posing as her grandson, she and her assisted-living pal hop on a motorized scooter and begin a perilous journey across Los Angeles to recover her money. ⁠
⁠
Oscar-nominee June Squibb (NEBRASKA) proves to be the summer’s most unlikely action hero in this Sundance breakout, also starring Malcolm McDowell, Parker Posey, Clark Gregg, and Richard Roundtree (SHAFT) in his final role.⁠
⁠
Get tickets at the link in our bio!⁠
⁠
#thelma #junesquibb #bmfi #brynmawrfilminstitute ⁠".
